&lt;p&gt;Traveling with a Dominica passport opens up a world of opportunities, allowing its holders to explore a variety of countries across the globe with relative ease. As of April 2026, Dominica passport holders can travel to 199 destinations, with varying visa requirements. This comprehensive guide will help you navigate the visa landscape, detailing where you can travel without a visa, where you can obtain a visa on arrival, and where you need to apply for a visa in advance.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>